title: DDFP: Dave Karaoke's with TJ Houshmandzadeh...sorta.
itunes:title: DDFP: Dave Karaoke's with TJ Houshmandzadeh...sorta.
description:
Shek & Rank track down Carson Palmer's former teammate/recent workout partner TJ Houshmandzadeh to discuss the state of the new Raider QB's elbow; cleaning his shoes with a Terrible Towel; and what music he listens to when he works out. Plus, the fellas debate the likelihood of Green Bay going undefeated; the Harbaugh/Schwartz Jim-Broglio; and England's own Handsome Hank stops in for a preview of Bucs/Bears and a discussion about the war of words between Rex Ryan & Norv Turner. And to wrap things, the guys take the DeLorean up to 88mph and travel to next Tuesday to see how eight Week Seven games turn out.
